'''控制传染源'''（又称'''管理传染源'''，{{Lang-en|Source control}}）是一种通过阻止[[传染病|传染病]]感染者在[[说话|说话]]、[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]或[[噴嚏|打喷嚏]]过程中产生{{Le|呼吸道分泌物|Respiratory droplet}}来减少疾病传播的策略<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=FAQs on the Emergency Use Authorization for Face Masks (Non-Surgical)|url=https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/emergency-situations-medical-devices/faqs-emergency-use-authorization-face-masks-non-surgical|accessdate=2020-05-21|author=|date=2020-04-26|first=|work=U.S. [[Food_and_Drug_Administration|Food and Drug Administration]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527140234/https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/emergency-situations-medical-devices/faqs-emergency-use-authorization-face-masks-non-surgical|archivedate=2020-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。通常[[外科口罩|外科口罩]]便起到了这个作用，除非是缺乏外科口罩，否则不建议公众使用[[布口罩|布口罩]]来应对[[流行病|流行病]]。<ref name=":12">{{Cite web|title=Using face masks in the community - Reducing COVID-19 transmission from potentially asymptomatic or pre-symptomatic people through the use of face masks|url=https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/using-face-masks-community-reducing-covid-19-transmission|accessdate=2020-05-21|author=|date=2020-04-08|first=|format=|work=[[歐洲疾病預防控制中心|European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control]]|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421224721/https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/using-face-masks-community-reducing-covid-19-transmission|archivedate=2020-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="interim2">{{Cite web|title=Interim Infection Prevention and Control Recommendations for Patients with Suspected or Confirmed Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) in Healthcare Settings|url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/hcp/infection-control-recommendations.html|accessdate=2020-05-21|author=|date=2020-05-18|first=|work=U.S. [[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]]|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605015900/https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/hcp/infection-control-recommendations.html|archivedate=2020-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，咳嗽时用[[面紙|面纸]]覆盖口鼻等也是控制传染源的一项举措。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Using face masks in the community - Reducing COVID-19 transmission from potentially asymptomatic or pre-symptomatic people through the use of face masks|url=https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/using-face-masks-community-reducing-covid-19-transmission|accessdate=2020-05-21|author=|date=2020-04-08|first=|format=|work=[[歐洲疾病預防控制中心|European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control]]|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421224721/https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/using-face-masks-community-reducing-covid-19-transmission|archivedate=2020-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>控制传染源属于预防传染病的三个基本措施（控制传染病的主要方法）之一，另外两个分别是[[切断传播途径|切断传播途径]]和[[保护易感人群|保护易感人群]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=HIV感染者/AIDS病人在低流行区的管理|author=王朝才 刘燕 马永成 王学文 樊明|url=http://www.wanfangdata.com.cn/details/detail.do?_type=perio&id=zgazbxb201004025|journal=中国艾滋病性病|issue=4|doi=|others=|year=2010|volume=16|page=415-416|pmid=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-02/16/c_1125582651.htm|title=控制传染源、切断传播途径、保护易感人群，这些关键举措一个都不少|author=熊丰 陈聪|date=2020-02-16|work=新华社“新华视点”微博|publisher=[[新华社|新华社]]|accessdate=2020-07-18|language=|format=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217143358/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2020-02/16/c_1125582651.htm|archive-date=2020-02-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=《黄帝内经》奠定了现代传染病学的基础|author=韩新平|url=http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/Conference_7145014.aspx|journal=全国第七届中医药继承创新与发展研讨会论文集|issue=|doi=|others=|year=2008-11-01|volume=|page=296|pmid=}}</ref>。

== 与个人防护设备的对比 ==
控制传染源可以保护其他人免受穿戴者的伤害，而{{Le|个人防护设备|Personal protective equipment}}也有类似功效。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Meat and Poultry Processing Workers and Employers: Interim Guidance from CDC and the Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA)|url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/organizations/meat-poultry-processing-workers-employers.html|accessdate=2020-05-24|author=|date=2020-05-12|first=|work=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507204916/https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/organizations/meat-poultry-processing-workers-employers.html|archivedate=2020-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[布口罩|布质口罩]]可用于控制传染源，但由于过滤效率低（通常在2％至60％之间）<ref name=":12" /><ref name="RengasamySamy2010">{{Cite journal|title=Simple Respiratory Protection—Evaluation of the Filtration Performance of Cloth Masks and Common Fabric Materials Against 20–1000 nm Size Particles|author=|url=|journal=Annals of Occupational Hygiene|publisher=Oxford University Press|issue=|doi=10.1093/annhyg/meq044|others=|year=2010|volume=54|page=|pages=789-798|issn=0003-4878|pmid=|quote=The results showed that cloth masks and other fabric materials tested in the study had 40–90% instantaneous penetration levels against polydisperse NaCl aerosols employed in the National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health particulate respirator test protocol at 5.5 cm s<sup>−1</sup>.|number=7}}</ref>，尽管它们易于获得且在清洗后可重复使用，但它们不被认为是个人防护设备<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=FAQs on the Emergency Use Authorization for Face Masks (Non-Surgical)|url=https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/emergency-situations-medical-devices/faqs-emergency-use-authorization-face-masks-non-surgical|accessdate=2020-05-21|author=|date=2020-04-26|first=|work=U.S. [[Food_and_Drug_Administration|Food and Drug Administration]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527140234/https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/emergency-situations-medical-devices/faqs-emergency-use-authorization-face-masks-non-surgical|archivedate=2020-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自制的布口罩没有任何标准或规定。<ref name=":1" />

[[外科口罩|外科口罩]]旨在防止飞溅和喷雾<ref name="interim2" />，但由于面罩表面与面部之间的配合较松散，因此无法为[[病原体|细菌]]和其他污染物提供完整的呼吸保护。<ref name=":23">{{Cite web|title=N95 Respirators and Surgical Masks (Face Masks)|url=http://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/personal-protective-equipment-infection-control/n95-respirators-and-surgical-masks-face-masks|accessdate=2020-05-23|author=|date=2020-04-05|first=|work=U.S. Food and Drug Administration|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328004254/https://www.fda.gov/medical-devices/personal-protective-equipment-infection-control/n95-respirators-and-surgical-masks-face-masks|archivedate=2020-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[外科口罩|外科口罩]]受到各种国家标准的监管，具有很高的[[細菌過濾率|细菌过滤率]]。<ref name="standards">{{Cite web|title=Comparison of Mask Standards, Ratings, and Filtration Effectiveness|url=https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/comparison-mask-standards-rating-effectiveness/|author=Robertson|date=2020-03-15|first=Paddy|work=Smart Air Filters|access-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711203308/https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/comparison-mask-standards-rating-effectiveness/|archive-date=2020-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中华人民共和国医药行业标准：YY 0469–2011 医用外科口罩|url=http://www.hz-rush.com/UploadFile/file/2020216171020.pdf|accessdate=2020-07-18|author=国家食品药品监督管理总局|date=|format=pdf|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031014212/http://www.hz-rush.com/UploadFile/file/2020216171020.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中华人民共和国医药行业标准：YY/T 0969–2013 一次性使用医用口罩|url=http://www.hz-rush.com/UploadFile/file/2020216170744.pdf|accessdate=2020-07-18|author=国家食品药品监督管理总局|date=|format=pdf|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031012242/http://www.hz-rush.com/UploadFile/file/2020216170744.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[N95口罩|N95口罩]]和其他[[自吸过滤式呼吸器|过滤式面罩呼吸器]]除了可以提供呼吸保护外，还可以提供源控制，但是带有排气阀的呼吸器可能不提供源控制<ref name="interim2" />。 

